params.name: artists_file
params.description: Path to the vocabulary file which contains a mapping between artists and ids. The default file supportsboth v2 and v3

params.name: genres_file
params.description: Path to the vocabulary file which contain a mapping between genres and ids.

params.name: lyrics_file
params.description: Path to the vocabulary file which contains the accepted characters for the lyrics tokenization.

params.name: version
params.description: List of the tokenizer versions. The 5b-lyricss top level prior model was trained using v3 instead ofv2.

params.name: n_genres
params.description: Maximum number of genres to use for composition.

params.name: max_n_lyric_tokens
params.description: Maximum number of lyric tokens to keep.

params.name: unk_token
params.description: The unknown token. A token that is not in the vocabulary cannot be converted to an ID and is set to be thistoken instead.
